SubjectSETTING APART Ochapowace Band (SK) Reserve No. 71-132
PrecisSetting apart of 95.952 hectares (237.10 acres) of surface lands and 114.628 hectares (283.25 acres) of mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the OCHAPOWACE BAND as Ochapowace Indian Reserve No. 71-132, located in the Rural Municipality of Edenwold No. 158, near Regina, Saskatchewan.
